d2","tid":1552531,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8470a868da3f35840316cd8d88a725dbf6a23801","tid":1552531,"uid":90450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:37:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.finehomebuilding.com/2009/08/11/code-change-alert-fire-sprinklers-in-all-new-homes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.finehomebuilding.com%2F2009%2F08%2F11%2Fcode-change-alert-fire-sprinklers-in-all-new-homes&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK7Xqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=881749f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.finehomebuilding.com/2009/08/11/code-change-alert-fire-sprinklers-in-all-new-homes</a><br />\n<br />\n燒爆D 消防頭,  淋濕D 閘機/LED DISPLAY, 救都有排<br />\n<br />\n消暑又可滑9 暴走速龍狗"}]}